00:48:09,235 --> 00:48:10,785
Get up, man!

802
00:48:12,635 --> 00:48:14,380
Come on, buddy.

803
00:48:15,700 --> 00:48:17,040
I got you.

804
00:48:17,075 --> 00:48:18,380
I got you...

