00:48:21,615 --> 00:48:22,945
No!

807
00:48:29,580 --> 00:48:31,820
Eat, eat!

808
00:48:31,855 --> 00:48:33,020
Eat!

809
00:48:36,780 --> 00:48:39,140
Bastardo.

