812
00:48:59,052 --> 00:49:01,220
We've got to get him
out of here.

813
00:49:01,255 --> 00:49:02,305
It's difficult.

814
00:49:02,340 --> 00:49:03,340
He's under
constant guard.

815
00:49:03,375 --> 00:49:05,465
Woman, here!

816
00:49:05,500 --> 00:49:07,465
A share goes to us!

817
00:49:07,500 --> 00:49:10,860
You, get us
some more food, now!

818
00:49:25,775 --> 00:49:28,277
I got you.

819
00:49:28,312 --> 00:49:30,780
I got you...

820
00:49:48,820 --> 00:49:51,385
I'm sorry, I'm sorry...

821
00:49:51,420 --> 00:49:52,665
<i>It was an accident...</i>

822
00:49:52,700 --> 00:49:54,580
<i>You can't keep
beating yourself up over it</i>

823
00:49:54,615 --> 00:49:55,540
<i>Your entire life.</i>

824
00:49:55,575 --> 00:49:56,700
I'm sorry.

825
00:50:07,220 --> 00:50:08,580
I'm coming, baby.

826
00:50:22,055 --> 00:50:22,980
You.

827
00:50:25,420 --> 00:50:27,625
Where's Jessie?

828
00:50:27,660 --> 00:50:30,220
She's still
waiting for you, Matt.

829
00:50:30,255 --> 00:50:33,105
She needs you.

830
00:50:33,140 --> 00:50:36,185
Get to the river and find Sam.

831
00:50:36,220 --> 00:50:39,820
He'll help you,
but you must find Sam.

832
00:50:42,540 --> 00:50:43,340
Sam.

